HEADWORD: Stinger
<hw>Sting"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, stings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Professor E. Forbes states that only a small minority of the
medusae of our seas are <qex>stingers</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Owen.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

